31st Street, at the N.W. corner of 30th Drive, showing the Hellenic Orthodox Community Church of Astoria and St. Demetrios. The view is northeastward from the 30th Drive toward 31st Street on which is the I.R.T. "El." Across the latter appears the steeple of the Second Reformed Church of Astoria.
View 2 is from the corner of 30th Street.
